-- Sky Italia to Match Mediaset Price for Italian Soccer Package, FT Reports
-- Ben Martin
-- 2010-06-28T02:27:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/sky-italia-to-match-mediaset-soccer-package-pricing-financial-times-says.html

          
          
             News Corp. ’s Sky Italia SpA will set
a 29-euro ($35.9) per month entry point for its coverage of
Italy’s Serie A soccer league, in a move that matches  Mediaset
SpA ’s list price for its own pay-TV soccer package, the
Financial Times reported, citing  Tom Mockridge , chief executive
officer of Sky Italia.  
